cemex sab de cv
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Materials
Industry: Construction Materials
Sub-Industry: Cement & Aggregates
Cemex SAB de CV is a building products company. The Company produces, distributes, and markets cement, ready-mix concrete, aggregates, and related building materials. Cemex operates throughout the Americas, Europe, Africa, the Middle East, and Asia.




