Company Description                    




                        Cemex S.A.B. de C.V., founded in 1906, is a leading producer and marketer of cement, ready-mix concrete,aggregate and related building materials. It operates internationally on a several continents including North America, Europe, Asia, South and Central America, the Caribbean and the Middle East. It has two divisions: Cemex Concreto and Cemex Cemento, as well as a large infrastructure represented by 66 cement facilities, 2000 concrete facilities, 400 aggregates quarries, 260 land distribution centers and 80 marine terminals.                    


